  <exercise>
    <statement>
      <p>
        If <m>A\vv=2\vv</m> for unknown <m>A</m> matrix and <m>\vv</m> vector,
        determine an expression for <m>A^2 \vv</m>,
        <m>A^3\vv</m>, <ellipsis/>, <m>A^m\vv</m>.
      </p>
    </statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>A^m \vv = 2^m \vv</m>
      </p>
